{
  "texts": [
    "DQN use a deep neural network to compute the reward for each action.",
    "Examples of application are: robotics, autonomous vehicles, faster video loading (Le et al. 2022a).",
    "DQN can be used in multiple tasks, but defining possible actions provides limited freedom, and may not be sufficient to tackle reality.",
    "Reinforcement learning also requires many observations for training.",
    "Some advances attempt to bridge the gap between text processing and computer vision."
  ]
}